sequenceDiagram
    box Route Processor
        participant CP as BGP / Zebra
        participant K as Kernel
        participant FPM as fpmsyncd
        participant PST as ProducerStateTable
        participant APP as APPL_DB
        participant ZMQ as ZMQ Server
    end
    box Line Card — one NPU
        participant ZC as zmqClient
        participant RO as RouteOrch
        participant HW as ASIC
    end

    CP->>CP: 1. Route_Install_Request
    CP->>K: 2. kernel route
    CP->>FPM: 3. FPM route
    FPM->>PST: invoke ProducerStateTable
    rect rgb(248, 250, 252)
        Note over PST,APP: ProducerStateTable
        PST->>APP: 4. update ROUTE_TABLE (Redis)
    end
    APP->>ZMQ: 5. publish to ZMQ Server
    ZMQ->>ZC: ZMQ IPC (midplane)
    ZC->>RO: consume route
    RO->>HW: 6. program route (SAI)
    Note over ZC,HW: Same view per NPU — each ASIC has its own zmqClient, RouteOrch, ASIC stack
